## Work Classification

Before starting, ask: **"Is this 1 task or 3+ related tasks?"**

### Single Task

```javascript
task = create_task({title: "Fix validation bug in handlers.{{EXT}}", status: "in_progress"})
// Do the work
log_progress({what: "Fixed validation in handlers.{{EXT}}:234"})
complete_task({task_id, status: "done"})
```

### 3+ Related Tasks — Create a Plan First

**The 3-Task Rule:** When you're about to create the third related task, stop. Create a plan first.

[CUSTOMIZE] Adjust this threshold (2+, 4+) based on your project. 3+ is recommended.

**Sequence matters:** Plan -> Document -> Tasks -> Link

[OPTIONAL: With MCP tools]
```javascript
// 1. Create plan
plan = save_plan({
  plan_id: "plan-{{FEATURE_ID}}",
  title: "{{FEATURE_SET}}",
  status: "in_progress",
  problem: "What problem this solves",
  goal: "What you're achieving",
  approach: "Technical strategy"
})

// 2. Document IMMEDIATELY
doc = save_document({
  document_id: "doc-{{FEATURE_ID}}-plan",
  project_id: "{{PROJECT_ID}}",
  title: "{{FEATURE_SET}} - Implementation Plan",
  doc_type: "plan_details",
  content: `
# Goal
[Specific deliverable]

# Approach
[Technical strategy, stack, patterns]

# Task Breakdown
1. Task one - ~30min
2. Task two - ~20min
3. Task three - ~25min

# Success Criteria
- [ ] Measurable criterion 1
- [ ] Measurable criterion 2

# Key Decisions
- Decision X because Y
`
})

// 3. Create tasks under the plan
task1 = save_task({plan_id: plan.plan_id, title: "Task 1", status: "todo"})
task2 = save_task({plan_id: plan.plan_id, title: "Task 2", status: "todo"})
task3 = save_task({plan_id: plan.plan_id, title: "Task 3", status: "todo"})

// 4. Link document to all tasks
link_document({
  document_id: doc.document_id,
  task_ids: [task1.task_id, task2.task_id, task3.task_id]
})

// 5. Check progress anytime
get_plan({plan_id: plan.plan_id})
```

[ALTERNATIVE: Without MCP tools]
```javascript
EnterPlanMode()
// Write plan to docs/plans/PLAN_{{FEATURE_ID}}.md
// Create tasks using TaskCreate
TaskCreate({subject: "Task 1", description: "...", activeForm: "Working on task 1"})
TaskCreate({subject: "Task 2", description: "...", activeForm: "Working on task 2"})
TaskCreate({subject: "Task 3", description: "...", activeForm: "Working on task 3"})
```

### Complex Work (Unclear Scope)

Create a parent task FIRST, then plan, then create subtasks:

```javascript
parent = create_task({title: "Add {{FEATURE}} to {{COMPONENT}}", status: "in_progress"})
// Now plan — the parent task tracks the entire effort including planning
EnterPlanMode()
